```

---

## Tests attendus

### Tests unitaires

Ajouter ou mettre à jour :

```text
test_aspect_calculation_contracts.py
test_aspect_runtime_builder.py
test_aspect_interpretive_hint_resolver.py
test_chart_interpretation_input_builder.py
test_chart_json_builder.py
